summary: Multilingual intersectional feminist safeguarding professional with background in psychology, gender & conflict. Experienced in supporting humanitarian and development organisations, teams & individuals to prevent and address safeguarding concerns and create a common culture of integrity. I am passionate for fighting injustices, value-driven, empathetic, hands-on and versatile. Pronouns: SHE/HER.
